# Package Management Rule

**Always use pnpm for all package management commands** - never npm or yarn.

This is a pnpm monorepo with workspaces defined in [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml).

Configuration files: [pnpm-lock.yaml](mdc:pnpm-lock.yaml) | [package.json](mdc:package.json)
